cky Oparah. In the opinion to information that went viral, the lovely actress holds an English Language degree, is apparently in love with Lucky and might likely end up walking down the aisle with him. The soft-spoken veteran screen diva didn’t debunk nor take part in the allegations of her lover boy, however, she said it was a disgusting report. “Sorry! This is the height of witchcraft! How demonic and absolutely disgusting. It is well. It’s really well,” she said. Vanguard News Nigeria